  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT318-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">kiḻavaṉ kēṭkum aṇmaiyaṉākat tōḻikkuk kiḻatti uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken by HER to the confidante, while HE was close
          [enough] to hear. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT318">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> eṟicuṟāk kalitta vilaṅkunīrp parappi</l>
          <l> ṉaṟuvī ñāḻaloṭu puṉṉai tāay</l>
          <l> veṟiyayar kaḷattiṉiṟ ṟōṉṟun tuṟaivaṉ</l>
          <l> kuṟiyā ṉāyiṉuṅ kuṟippiṉum piṟitoṉ</l>
          <l> ṟaṟiyārk kuraippalō yāṉē yeyttavip</l>
          <l> paṇaiyeḻiṉ meṉṟō ḷaṇaiiya vannāṭ</l>
          <l> piḻaiyā vañciṉañ ceyta</l>
          <l> kaḷvaṉuṅ kaṭavaṉum puṇaivaṉun tāṉē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>As for me, will I tell him who does not know</l>
          <l rend="indent2">that one thing is different , whether he intends it or not ,</l>
          <l>the man from the ghat, where in the expanse</l>
          <l rend="indent">the shining water, in which dashing sharks are thriving,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">after Puṉṉai has been spread together with Ñāḻal</l>
          <l rend="indent9">in fragrant blossoms,</l>
          <l rend="indent">appears like the floor, where they engage in the Veṟi dance,</l>
          <l>− him, who [is] robber and dutiful one and support,</l>
          <l>who has made an unfailing oath</l>
          <l rend="indent">that day he touched these soft shoulders with the grace of bamboo,</l>
          <l rend="indent6">that [now] have become weary?</l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="1-3b">
            <l>where the Puṉṉai trees with the Ñāḻal trees spreading fragrant blooms</l>
            <l>in the expanse of shining water, in which dashing sharks are thriving,</l>
            <l>appear like the floor, where they engage in the Veṟi dance,</l>
          </lg>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
